        "title": "fix(gateway): dedupe probe warnings by gateway identity",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Fixes #69135 by suppressing `multiple_gateways` only when reachable probe targets report the same provable gateway self identity.\n- Gateway self presence now exposes a process-level `instanceId`; same-host/same-config ambiguity without a process/device identity remains conservative and still warns.\n- SSH tunnel, proxy/TLS URL, and configured remote URL can resolve to the same gateway even when transport ports differ.\n- Docs and regression tests now describe distinct, same, and identity-ambiguous gateway cases.\n- No config surface or plugin API surface changed.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/system-presence.test.ts src/infra/system-presence.version.test.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.test.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.test.ts --reporter=dot` -> 4 files, 22 tests passed\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 src/infra/system-presence.ts docs/cli/gateway.md docs/gateway/index.md docs/gateway/multiple-gateways.md docs/gateway/troubleshooting.md src/commands/gateway-presence.test.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.test.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.ts`\n- `./node_modules/.bin/oxlint --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.core.json src/infra/system-presence.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.test.ts src/commands/gateway-presence.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.test.ts src/commands/gateway-status/output.ts` -> 0 warnings, 0 errors\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `codex review --base origin/main` -> no actionable correctness issues found\n\nRebased onto current `main` (`7ca77124fea04cdbb4308ee21b5cbd7af5d9a202`) for Dependency Guard. All 7 commits remain signed.\n\nSigned head: `97b81a20bd207e971f4b99701b20aa6405fcecc5`.\n",
